<p><strong>附录：监控录像</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">查看收容室监控录像</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
