<p><strong>附录：对话记录-B</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">开启对话记录-B</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
